{"pagelen": 100, "values": [{"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/vrx/issues/173/comments/54223390.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/vrx/issues/173#comment-54223390"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/vrx/issues/173.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 173, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/vrx.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/vrx"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{e278ca38-7edb-4e62-b785-46dff5617d98}ts=2274605"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "vrx", "full_name": "osrf/vrx", "uuid": "{e278ca38-7edb-4e62-b785-46dff5617d98}"}, "title": "ENU to NED Issues"}, "content": {"raw": null, "markup": "markdown", "html": "", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2019-10-06T12:06:37.462930+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Hashir Zahir", "uuid": "{0033cdb9-ea6e-4c6a-a9ad-d462a485643d}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B0033cdb9-ea6e-4c6a-a9ad-d462a485643d%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B0033cdb9-ea6e-4c6a-a9ad-d462a485643d%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/3c71628af17207fad1dd0ea6280b41f1d=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsHZ-5.png"}}, "nickname": "hzahir", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:6b6463b7-2835-47c7-8c22-fdef36e9e325"}, "updated_on": null, "type": "issue_comment", "id": 54223390}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/vrx/issues/173/comments/54223474.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/vrx/issues/173#comment-54223474"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/vrx/issues/173.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 173, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/vrx.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/vrx"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{e278ca38-7edb-4e62-b785-46dff5617d98}ts=2274605"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "vrx", "full_name": "osrf/vrx", "uuid": "{e278ca38-7edb-4e62-b785-46dff5617d98}"}, "title": "ENU to NED Issues"}, "content": {"raw": null, "markup": "markdown", "html": "", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2019-10-06T12:25:47.996501+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Hashir Zahir", "uuid": "{0033cdb9-ea6e-4c6a-a9ad-d462a485643d}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B0033cdb9-ea6e-4c6a-a9ad-d462a485643d%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B0033cdb9-ea6e-4c6a-a9ad-d462a485643d%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/3c71628af17207fad1dd0ea6280b41f1d=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsHZ-5.png"}}, "nickname": "hzahir", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:6b6463b7-2835-47c7-8c22-fdef36e9e325"}, "updated_on": null, "type": "issue_comment", "id": 54223474}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/vrx/issues/173/comments/54243927.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/vrx/issues/173#comment-54243927"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/vrx/issues/173.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 173, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/vrx.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/vrx"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{e278ca38-7edb-4e62-b785-46dff5617d98}ts=2274605"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "vrx", "full_name": "osrf/vrx", "uuid": "{e278ca38-7edb-4e62-b785-46dff5617d98}"}, "title": "ENU to NED Issues"}, "content": {"raw": "Yes, the [Hector IMU Gazebo plugin](http://wiki.ros.org/hector_gazebo_plugins) \\(used in VRX\\)  follows the ROS convention \\(see[ REP 103](https://www.ros.org/reps/rep-0103.html)\\) for the body frame to be reported in ENU.  It is very common to have a sensor that works in NED and have to adapt higher level code to deal cleanly with the conventions.  \n\nIt is difficult to recommend solutions specific to your setup without understanding more about your setup.  Could you add images of your tf tree and ROS graph?  That might help folks give you advice.\n\n\u200c", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Yes, the <a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"http://wiki.ros.org/hector_gazebo_plugins\" rel=\"nofollow\">Hector IMU Gazebo plugin</a> (used in VRX)  follows the ROS convention (see<a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"https://www.ros.org/reps/rep-0103.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"> REP 103</a>) for the body frame to be reported in ENU.  It is very common to have a sensor that works in NED and have to adapt higher level code to deal cleanly with the conventions.  </p>\n<p>It is difficult to recommend solutions specific to your setup without understanding more about your setup.  Could you add images of your tf tree and ROS graph?  That might help folks give you advice.</p>\n<p>\u200c</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2019-10-07T19:47:38.563703+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Brian Bingham", "uuid": "{9cdea257-248f-486e-8858-49d8485a916f}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B9cdea257-248f-486e-8858-49d8485a916f%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B9cdea257-248f-486e-8858-49d8485a916f%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:6c52d6e5-77e0-41a8-8b6e-cb9462f4d5f1/7a690884-fc47-4bca-9c2b-baecee4d3dc9/128"}}, "nickname": "brian_bingham", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:6c52d6e5-77e0-41a8-8b6e-cb9462f4d5f1"}, "updated_on": null, "type": "issue_comment", "id": 54243927}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/vrx/issues/173/comments/54320017.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/vrx/issues/173#comment-54320017"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/vrx/issues/173.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 173, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/vrx.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/vrx"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{e278ca38-7edb-4e62-b785-46dff5617d98}ts=2274605"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "vrx", "full_name": "osrf/vrx", "uuid": "{e278ca38-7edb-4e62-b785-46dff5617d98}"}, "title": "ENU to NED Issues"}, "content": {"raw": "Sorry for the late reply. Issue was resolved after debugging the TF tree of our code base. For others who may face this issue,  just need to perform a rotation of PI in x-axis and rotation in -PI/2 in the z axis when converting between the 2 frames. Thanks.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Sorry for the late reply. Issue was resolved after debugging the TF tree of our code base. For others who may face this issue,  just need to perform a rotation of PI in x-axis and rotation in -PI/2 in the z axis when converting between the 2 frames. Thanks.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2019-10-13T02:31:35.824514+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Hashir Zahir", "uuid": "{0033cdb9-ea6e-4c6a-a9ad-d462a485643d}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B0033cdb9-ea6e-4c6a-a9ad-d462a485643d%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B0033cdb9-ea6e-4c6a-a9ad-d462a485643d%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/3c71628af17207fad1dd0ea6280b41f1d=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsHZ-5.png"}}, "nickname": "hzahir", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:6b6463b7-2835-47c7-8c22-fdef36e9e325"}, "updated_on": null, "type": "issue_comment", "id": 54320017}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/vrx/issues/173/comments/54320020.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/vrx/issues/173#comment-54320020"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/vrx/issues/173.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 173, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/vrx.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/vrx"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{e278ca38-7edb-4e62-b785-46dff5617d98}ts=2274605"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "vrx", "full_name": "osrf/vrx", "uuid": "{e278ca38-7edb-4e62-b785-46dff5617d98}"}, "title": "ENU to NED Issues"}, "content": {"raw": "Issue has been resolved", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Issue has been resolved</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2019-10-13T02:31:53.016634+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Hashir Zahir", "uuid": "{0033cdb9-ea6e-4c6a-a9ad-d462a485643d}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B0033cdb9-ea6e-4c6a-a9ad-d462a485643d%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B0033cdb9-ea6e-4c6a-a9ad-d462a485643d%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/3c71628af17207fad1dd0ea6280b41f1d=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsHZ-5.png"}}, "nickname": "hzahir", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:6b6463b7-2835-47c7-8c22-fdef36e9e325"}, "updated_on": null, "type": "issue_comment", "id": 54320020}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/vrx/issues/173/comments/54366800.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/vrx/issues/173#comment-54366800"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/vrx/issues/173.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 173, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/vrx.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/vrx"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{e278ca38-7edb-4e62-b785-46dff5617d98}ts=2274605"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "vrx", "full_name": "osrf/vrx", "uuid": "{e278ca38-7edb-4e62-b785-46dff5617d98}"}, "title": "ENU to NED Issues"}, "content": {"raw": "I\u2019m glad you were able to resolve the issue.  Any chance you could point to a snippet of code that fixed this problem for your case?  I imagine that this would be useful to others with similar issues.\n\nThank you for marking this resolved.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>I\u2019m glad you were able to resolve the issue.  Any chance you could point to a snippet of code that fixed this problem for your case?  I imagine that this would be useful to others with similar issues.</p>\n<p>Thank you for marking this resolved.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2019-10-15T20:46:06.548068+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Brian Bingham", "uuid": "{9cdea257-248f-486e-8858-49d8485a916f}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B9cdea257-248f-486e-8858-49d8485a916f%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B9cdea257-248f-486e-8858-49d8485a916f%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:6c52d6e5-77e0-41a8-8b6e-cb9462f4d5f1/7a690884-fc47-4bca-9c2b-baecee4d3dc9/128"}}, "nickname": "brian_bingham", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:6c52d6e5-77e0-41a8-8b6e-cb9462f4d5f1"}, "updated_on": null, "type": "issue_comment", "id": 54366800}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/vrx/issues/173/comments/54403906.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/vrx/issues/173#comment-54403906"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/vrx/issues/173.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 173, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/vrx.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/vrx"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{e278ca38-7edb-4e62-b785-46dff5617d98}ts=2274605"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "vrx", "full_name": "osrf/vrx", "uuid": "{e278ca38-7edb-4e62-b785-46dff5617d98}"}, "title": "ENU to NED Issues"}, "content": {"raw": "Sure. I utilized the tf static publisher and published an additional transform between base\\_link and my odom frame. In a launch file, it will look something like this:  \n\n```\n<node pkg=\"tf2_ros\" type=\"static_transform_publisher\" name=\"enu_ned_broadcast\" \n            args=\"0 0 0 3.14 0 -1.57 map base_link\" />\n```\n\nfollowing syntax \n\n```\nstatic_transform_publisher x y z yaw pitch roll frame_id child_frame_id\n```\n\nfrom [http://wiki.ros.org/tf2\\_ros](http://wiki.ros.org/tf2_ros). It seems to have worked, although I am not sure if it is the most optimal solution.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Sure. I utilized the tf static publisher and published an additional transform between base_link and my odom frame. In a launch file, it will look something like this:  </p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span>&lt;node pkg=&quot;tf2_ros&quot; type=&quot;static_transform_publisher&quot; name=&quot;enu_ned_broadcast&quot; \n            args=&quot;0 0 0 3.14 0 -1.57 map base_link&quot; /&gt;\n</pre></div>\n\n\n<p>following syntax </p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span>static_transform_publisher x y z yaw pitch roll frame_id child_frame_id\n</pre></div>\n\n\n<p>from <a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"http://wiki.ros.org/tf2_ros\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://wiki.ros.org/tf2_ros</a>. It seems to have worked, although I am not sure if it is the most optimal solution.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2019-10-17T17:57:57.944685+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Hashir Zahir", "uuid": "{0033cdb9-ea6e-4c6a-a9ad-d462a485643d}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B0033cdb9-ea6e-4c6a-a9ad-d462a485643d%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B0033cdb9-ea6e-4c6a-a9ad-d462a485643d%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/3c71628af17207fad1dd0ea6280b41f1d=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsHZ-5.png"}}, "nickname": "hzahir", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:6b6463b7-2835-47c7-8c22-fdef36e9e325"}, "updated_on": "2019-10-17T18:43:23.841753+00:00", "type": "issue_comment", "id": 54403906}, {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/vrx/issues/173/comments/54404338.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/vrx/issues/173#comment-54404338"}}, "issue": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/vrx/issues/173.json"}}, "type": "issue", "id": 173, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/vrx.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/vrx"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{e278ca38-7edb-4e62-b785-46dff5617d98}ts=2274605"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "vrx", "full_name": "osrf/vrx", "uuid": "{e278ca38-7edb-4e62-b785-46dff5617d98}"}, "title": "ENU to NED Issues"}, "content": {"raw": "Nice!  Thank you.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Nice!  Thank you.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2019-10-17T18:43:34.807282+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Brian Bingham", "uuid": "{9cdea257-248f-486e-8858-49d8485a916f}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B9cdea257-248f-486e-8858-49d8485a916f%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B9cdea257-248f-486e-8858-49d8485a916f%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:6c52d6e5-77e0-41a8-8b6e-cb9462f4d5f1/7a690884-fc47-4bca-9c2b-baecee4d3dc9/128"}}, "nickname": "brian_bingham", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:6c52d6e5-77e0-41a8-8b6e-cb9462f4d5f1"}, "updated_on": null, "type": "issue_comment", "id": 54404338}], "page": 1, "size": 8}